\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 4\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Now he had to go through Samaria.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So he came to a town in Samaria called Sychar, near the plot of ground Jacob had given to his son Joseph.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 6\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jacob\'92s well was there, and Jesus, tired as he was from the journey, sat down by the well. It was about noon.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 7\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When a Samaritan woman came to draw water, \
\
Jesus said to her,\'a0\'93Will you give me a drink?\'94\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub (His disciples had gone into the town\'a0to buy food.)\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The Samaritan woman said to him, \'93You are a Jew and I am a Samaritan\'a0woman. How can you ask me for a drink?\'94 (For Jews do not associate with Samaritans.
\fs15 \super [\ul a\ulnone ]
\fs24 \nosupersub )\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus Broke Barriers\'85\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl1
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He broke man made rules \'96 Jews don\'92t talk to Samaritans, and men don\'92t talk to women, and good people definitely don\'92t talk to bad people.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He went to where people were \'96 the church has messed this up for far too long\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He didn\'92t care what other people think\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus answered her,\'a0\'93If you knew the gift of God and who it is that asks you for a drink, you would have asked him and he would have given you living water.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can we be honest and just admit that this is a little odd.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He asks her for a drink then tells her she\'92s doing it wrong.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 11\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Sir,\'94 the woman said, \'93you have nothing to draw with and the well is deep. Where can you get this living water?\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 12\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Are you greater than our father Jacob, who gave us the well\'a0and drank from it himself, as did also his sons and his livestock?\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus answered,\'a0\'93Everyone who drinks this water will be thirsty again,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub but whoever drinks the water I give them will never thirst.\'a0Indeed, the water I give them will become in them a spring of water\'a0welling up to eternal life.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This seems like another odd thing to say but he is getting to some of her deep seated insecurities he struggles with.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Because every day she has to get up and decide when she\'92s going to get water.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every day she gets up and decides if she is going to deal with her past\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf4 \super 15\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The woman said to him, \'93Sir, give me this water so that I won\'92t get thirsty\'a0and have to keep coming here to draw water.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am done with this feeling I have\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I am done and want to move on with my life\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t want to see those people ever again\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Help me get past this situation.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4\b \cf5 Transition:  And then Jesus does something that seems so incredibly rude and offensive\'85it\'92s a good thing he doesn\'92t care about what others think huh?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 16\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub He told her,\'a0\'93Go, call your husband and come back.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 17\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93I have no husband,\'94 she replied.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m single\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 Jesus said to her,\'a0\'93You are right when you say you have no husband.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 18\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The fact is, you have had five husbands, and the man you now have is not your husband. What you have just said is quite true.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus just called her out in her sin\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Now a few things you need to know to get a really good picture of why she would have shame.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Women weren\'92t allowed to get a divorce\'85it\'92s not like now.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So what does that mean?  She was married, and left\'85and married and then left\'85and married and then left\'85and married and then left\'85and married and then left\'85over and over.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And what is communicated is you have very little value to anyone.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And so she find herself in this situation where she never wanted to be when she was growing up but there she is\'85living with a guy, hoping he won\'92t be like the others, avoiding other women because of her shame, and now Jesus is calling her out on it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs21 \cf6 \'93\'85your past is not your past if it\'92s still impacting your present\'94\'a0 Pete Wilson\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f4\b\fs24 \cf5 Transition:  Then they have a conversation about worship that leads to this\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
