\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf4 \super 25\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The woman said, \'93I know that Messiah\'94 (called Christ)\'a0\'93is coming. When he comes, he will explain everything to us.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 26\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then Jesus declared,\'a0\'93I, the one speaking to you\'97I am he.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 28\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then, leaving her water jar, the woman went back to the town and said to the people,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 29\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Come, see a man who told me everything I ever did.\'a0Could this be the Messiah?\'94\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 30\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub They came out of the town and made their way toward him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Here is the crazy part\'85she thought this day was like any other day going to the well.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What she found was that her life could have a bigger meaning, a bigger impact, and God wasn\'92t done with her.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Her past was her past but it didn\'92t dictate her future.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Today is a day you can have an encounter with God and allow Him, not you\'85you\'92ve been trying for years and failed\'85allow HIM to change you!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can be a difference maker\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
